{"tid":2207772,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"(2006年訪問)錫住李嘉欣　劉鑾雄：我吔經得起考驗","createTime":"2020-09-18T11:23:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-18T12:42:53.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"569ec633bd6753e640d61c3f1e487be6ee3f6062","tid":2207772,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T11:23:20.000Z","msg":"節錄:<br />\n大劉更強調，他絕不是擲錢包女星的富豪。反而當年他為博紅顏一笑，不惜做牛做馬，跑上跑落，關係絕非建基於金錢之上。<br />\n「我好記得九一年華東水災期間，有日嘉欣住的樂陶苑停電，但佢又要飛，所以我跑廿幾層樓幫佢搬行李落。另一次又係佢屋企停電，但佢話想食麻蓉飽，我又專登拎住盒新鮮熱辣的麻蓉包跑上廿幾層樓俾佢食，佢好感動。今日叫我做番，我都未必有咁氣力。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.nextmgz.com/archive/article/851/6072687\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farchive%2Farticle%2F851%2F6072687&d=U3in%2BbByR8w%2FZmejrHnAdSHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=25c47593\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farchive%2Farticle%2F851%2F6072687&h=cd71d693\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.nextmgz.com/archive/article/851/6072687</a>"},{"pid":"e387e9503db9c372ab7b17665792a8430478817e","tid":2207772,"uid":344567,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T11:29:02.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">開係絕非建基金錢之上</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原來咁撚聰明嘅男人都會係會喺女人方面咁高估自己"},{"pid":"f98a44df76d6dc2a3a4ededaa098a400615f3ded","tid":2207772,"uid":370409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T11:48:49.000Z","msg":"恭"},{"pid":"0ad8605e06de0c08acebfcb9e1c6eb540c95b6eb","tid":2207772,"uid":68661,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T12:12:52.000Z","msg":"恭喜你當年咁好體力呀<br />\n跑上廿幾層樓梯買麻蓉包俾Michele食<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bb6cf9e91e569a63a87ace8fb2b0c767370a1db","tid":2207772,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f98a44df76d6dc2a3a4ededaa098a400615f3ded","tid":2207772,"uid":370409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T11:48:49.00